red%20values%3F%20Will%20I%20promote%20them%20in%20the%20examples%20that%20we%20set%20for%20the%20next%20generations%3F%20You%20are%20damn%20right%2C%20I%20will!%20Because%20that's%20my%20duty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20leader%20further%20said%20that%20as%20a%20president%20it%20will%20be%20his%20responsibility%20to%20make%20faith%2C%20family%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20patriotism%2C%20and%20faith%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20again%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20teachings%20is%20that%20we%20don't%20choose%20who%20God%20chooses%20to%20work%20through.%20That's%20not%20our%20choice%2C%20that%20belongs%20to%20God...so%20yes%20are%20founded%20on%20Judai-Christian%20values%20and%20these%20are%20values%20that%20I%20deeply%20share....as%20a%20president%2C%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20make%20faith%20and%20family%20and%20hard%20work%20and%20patriotism%2C%20but%20faith%20includes%2C%20cool%20again%20in%20this%20country%20for%20the%20next%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%2038-year-old%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20is%20a%20native%20of%20southwest%20Ohio.%20His%20mother%20was%20a%20geriatric%20psychiatrist%20and%20his%20father%20worked%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20General%20Electric.%20His%20parents%20migrated%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy's%20campaign%20has%20gained%20attention%2C%20and%20he%20has%20risen%20in%20GOP%20primary%20polls%2C%20although%20he%20still%20trails%20behind%20Trump%20and%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20in%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20US%20presidential%20election%20is%20scheduled%20for%20November%205%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700330400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fub0ng3eo_vivek-ramaswamy_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%