ith%20flowers%20for%20the%20'fidelity%20test'%2C%20as%20elders%20and%20villagers%20gathered%20to%20witness%20it%2C%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20woman's%2057-year-old%20husband%20had%20been%20suspecting%20her%20fidelity%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20finally%20took%20it%20up%20with%20the%20elders%20of%20his%20tribal%20community%20to%20put%20her%20wife's%20character%20to%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20husband%20had%20allegedly%20manhandled%20her%20several%20times%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20old%20custom%20of%20the%20Yerukula%20tribe%20to%20which%20they%20belong%2C%20the%20woman%20whose%20fidelity%20is%20being%20suspected%20should%20dip%20her%20hands%20in%20boiling%20oil%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20community%20members%20to%20see%20if%20her%20hands%20will%20get%20burnt%20or%20not%2C%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20the%20woman's%20hands%20do%20not%20get%20scalded%2C%20then%20the%20tribe%20will%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20she%20was%20faithful%20to%20her%20husband%20but%20if%20it%20does%20get%20burnt%2C%20then%20they%20will%20infer%20that%20she%20was%20'unfaithful'%2C%20said%20the%20official%20who%20intervened%20on%20a%20tip-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20with%20four%20grown%20up%20children%20agreed%20to%20go%20through%20this%20test%20to%20prove%20her%20fidelity%20and%20everything%20was%20ready%20when%20the%20local%20mandal%20parishad%20development%20officer%20(MPDO)%20arrived%20in%20time%20to%20stop%20this%20'custom'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20woman%20agreed%20to%20the%20test%20as%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20better%20to%20prove%20her%20innocence%20than%20regularly%20suffer%20from%20her%20husband's%20thrashing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20police%20case%20was%20booked%20against%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20this%20matter%20but%20the%20husband%20and%20other%20family%20members%