0transitions%20to%20a%20greener%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3B5%20Trends%20to%20Bet%20Your%20Career%20On%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Grant%20Holderman%2C%2018%2C%20who%20is%20training%20to%20become%20an%20electrician%20in%20New%20Hampshire.%20This%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%2018%20and%20live%20in%20New%20London%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%20in%20June.%20Even%20though%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20teachers%20talked%20about%20college%2C%20I%20just%20never%20felt%20it%20was%20the%20right%20path%20for%20me%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20into%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20music%20and%20playing%20guitar%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20turn%20a%20passion%20into%20a%20career.%20So%20when%20my%20parents%20hired%20a%20carpenter%2C%20they%20mentioned%20to%20him%20that%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20getting%20into%20the%20trades.%20The%20carpenter%20connected%20me%20to%20an%20electrician%20who%20was%20hiring%2C%20and%20he%20gave%20me%20the%20rundown%20of%20doing%20an%20apprenticeship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20I%20started%20working%20at%20his%20company%2C%20BT%20Morin%20Electric.%20I%20work%20more%20than%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20then%20do%20my%20online%20education%20at%20Vermont%20Technical%20College.%20On%20Mondays%20and%20Wednesdays%2C%20I%20have%20class%20from%205%3A30%20pm%20to%208%3A00%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%2040%20other%20people%20in%20my%20class%20%E2%80%94%20of%20all%20ages.%20Most%20are%20men%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20number%20of%20women%20who%20are%20enrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20four-year%20program.%20It%20only%20costs%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20which%20I'm%20paying.%20My%20boss%20at%20BT%20Morin%20Electric%20offered%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20education%2C%20but%20then%20I%20would%20owe%20him%20a%20couple%20years%20of%20working%20after%20I%20get%20my%20license.%20I'd%20like%20to%20move%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%20in%20school%20we're%20learning%20about%20safety%2C%20electrical%20codes%2C%20and%20residential%20wiring.%20But%20I'm%20learning%20the%20most%20by%20working.%20I%20feel%20like%20in%20just%20two%20months%20I've%20learned%20more%20than%20my%20entire%20time%20in%20high%20school.%20We're%20hooking%20up%20generators%2C%20and%20running%20wiring%20throughout%20homes%20to%20outlets%2C%20lights%2C%20and%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20it's%20like%20solving%20a%20puzzle.%20Just%20today%2C%20there%20wasn't%20power%20in%20one%20room%20of%20this%20house%20we%20were%20working%20in.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20find%20the%20source%20of%20the%20problem%20by%20testing%20wires%20and%20tracing%20the%20flow%20of%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20challenging%20part%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20guys%20I%20work%20with.%20We're%20a%20four-man%20crew.%20They%20like%20to%20mess%20with%20me%20because%20I'm%20the%20new%20guy.%20But%20I'm%20glad%20I%20get%20to%20wake%20up%20and%20go%20learn.%20It's%20just%20like%20school%2C%20except%20I'm%20getting%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20earn%20%2415.50%20an%20hour%20now.%20That%20should%20increase%20when%20I%20demonstrate%20that%20I%20can%20do%20the%20work%20on%20my%20own.%20Once%20I%20get%20my%20license%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20moving%20somewhere%20and%20potentially%20working%20at%20a%20bigger%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20get%20into%20the%20solar%20industry.%20I've%20done%20some%20research%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20why%20aren't%20we%20adding%20more%20solar%20than%20we%20are%20now%3F%20If%20I%20can%20use%20my%20skills%20to%20create%20a%20better%20world%2C%20I%20absolutely%20want%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20would%20feel%20good%20going%20to%20work%20knowing%20I'm%20helping%20solve%20a%20problem%20the%20Earth%20is%20facing.%20It'd%20be%20cool%20to%20come%20home%20and%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20created%20renewable%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-skip-four-year-college-become-electrician-no-student-loans-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700328354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e528db788914e5553ed42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-skip-four-year-college-become-electrician-no-student-loans-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grant%20Holderman%20knew%20college%20wasn't%20for%20him%20and%20is%20to%20be%20an%20electrician.%20%26quot%3BIt'd%20be%20cool%20to%20come%20home%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20I%20created%20renewable%20energy.'%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A139%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-skip-four-year-college-become-electrician-no-student-loans-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Consider%20getting%20trained%20to%20become%20an%20electrician%20%E2%80%94%20and%20fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20of%20an%20Outlet%20Transformation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65551bed36d588dc55d110ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Ryan%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElectricians%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20as%20the%20US%20transitions%20to%20a%20greener%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%2073%2C000%20jobs%20are%20expected%20to%20open%20each%20year%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3B5%20Trends%20to%20Bet%20Your%20Career%20On%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-oil-wants-to-become-big-electric-vehicle-charging-batteries-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAutomakers%20are%20churning%20out%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Solar%20panels%20and%20wind%20turbines%20are%20increasingly%20dotting%20the%20landscape.%20Homeowners%20and%20real-estate%20developers%20are%20leaning%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassive-house-energy-efficient-lower-utility-bills-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egreen%20buildings%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20signs%20everywhere%20that%20America%20is%20transitioning%20to%20a%20greener%20economy.%20To%20pick%20up%20the%20pace%2C%20the%20US%20needs%20thousands%20of%20new%20electricians%20to%20do%20much%20of%20the%20behind-the-scenes%20work%20like%20installing%20and%20maintaining%20charging%20stations%2C%20transmission%20lines%2C%20and%20electric%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20this%20revolution%20to%20get%20off%20gas%20and%20fossil%20fuels%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant%20Shmelzer%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Independent%20Electrical%20Contractors%20of%20Chesapeake%2C%20which%20runs%20an%20apprenticeship%20program%20in%20the%20Maryland-Virginia%20area.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20what%20the%20state%20and%20federal%20government%20is%20shooting%20for%2C%20it's%20all%20electric%20driven.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20is%20set%20to%20pour%20nearly%20%24400%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20into%20climate%20action%2C%20including%20tax%20breaks%20for%20solar%20and%20wind%20projects%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20electric%20appliances%20like%20heat%20pumps%2C%20and%20low-carbon%20manufacturing.%20There%20are%20new%20loans%20and%20grants%20for%20transmission%20lines.%20Two%20dozen%20states%20have%20set%20their%20own%20goals%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.c2es.org%2Fcontent%2Fstate-climate-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eslash%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20energy%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20data%20indicates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fooh%2Fconstruction-and-extraction%2Felectricians.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3Din%2520May%25202022.-%2CJob%2520Outlook%2Con%2520average%252C%2520over%2520the%2520decade.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eelectrician%20jobs%20are%20growing%20faster%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20the%20average%20of%20all%20occupations%2C%20with%2073%2C500%20openings%20expected%20each%20year%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20That's%20more%20than%20triple%20the%20projected%20number%20of%20yearly%20openings%20for%20physicians%20and%20surgeons.%20Some%20industry%20estimates%20suggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqmerit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhite-Paper-Electrification2030-Qmerit.pdf%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edemand%20for%20electricians%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20even%20higher%20now%20that%20incentives%20from%20the%20IRA%20are%20ramping%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsletter.businessinsider.com%2Fclick%2F32857048.1808%2FaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxzLmdvdi9vZXMvY3VycmVudC9vZXM0NzIxMTEuaHRtP3V0bV9tZWRpdW09bmV3c2xldHRlciZlbWFpbD1jYm91ZHJlYXUlNDBpbnNpZGVyLmNvbSZ4PTgxMjhlMjllMzA3ZDhjMjYyMjg3MGM0M2QyZTgzMWEyMmNlNTAwOTI1NWExNTBkNTQ3MTcwMzVlOGNiMGQwYTYjc3Q%2F628bdf90094963f5ad0eef3eBb92ed97b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emean%20annual%20wage%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20electricians%20in%202022%20was%20about%20%2465%2C000%2C%20but%20salaries%20vary%20by%20state.%20In%20California%2C%20a%20master%20electrician%20can%20make%20as%20much%20as%20an%20attorney%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20without%20racking%20up%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20said%20Tom%20Bowen%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Qmerit%2C%20a%20company%20in%20Irvine%20that%20connects%20homeowners%20and%20commercial%20properties%20with%20contractors%20who%20can%20install%20EV%20chargers%2C%20rooftop%20solar%20panels%2C%20and%20battery%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20about%203%2C500%20contractors%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20and%20is%20adding%20new%20contractors%20to%20its%20platform%20every%20day%2C%20Bowen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20there%20aren't%20enough%20trained%20electricians%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand%2C%20partly%20because%20they're%20retiring%20at%20a%20faster%20rate%20than%20they're%20entering%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20said%20that%20reversing%20the%20trend%20would%20require%20overcoming%20several%20cultural%20hurdles%20and%20investing%20in%20apprenticeship%20programs.%20Traditionally%20the%20trades%20have%20been%20dominated%20by%20white%20men%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatausa.io%2Fprofile%2Fsoc%2Felectricians%3Futm_medium%3Dnewsletter%26email%3Dcboudreau%2540insider.com%26x%3D8128e29e307d8c2622870c43d2e831a22ce5009255a150d54717035e8cb0d0a6%26utm_source%3DSailthru%26utm_campaign%3DInsider%2520Sustainability%252C%2520September%252028%252C%25202023%26utm_term%3DINSIDER%2520SUSTAINABILITY%2520SEND%2520LIST%23demographics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efederal%20data%20indicates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%202021%2C%20only%202%25%20of%20electricians%20were%20women%20and%20nearly%2080%25%20were%20white.%20Many%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%20also%20lack%20interest%20in%20these%20areas%20and%20are%20often%20told%20that%20a%20four-year%20college%20degree%20is%20the%20ticket%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20education%20system%20is%20still%20built%20on%20getting%20every%20student%20to%20go%20to%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20Shmelzer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-not-going-to-college-tuition-costs-higher-education-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAs%20Gen%20Zers%20rethink%20college%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20some%20states%20like%20Maryland%20are%20trying%20a%20different%20approach.%20It%20aims%20to%20have%2045%25%20of%20high%20schoolers%20go%20through%20an%20apprenticeship%20program%20or%20graduate%20with%20an%20industry-recognized%20credential%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShmelzer%20said%20the%20Independent%20Electrical%20Contractors%20of%20Chesapeake%20was%20pouring%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20into%20recruiting%20more%20high-school%20students%2C%20as%20well%20as%20career%20changers%20and%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20educates%20about%201%2C000%20people%20a%20year%20and%20places%20them%20in%20electrician%20apprenticeships%20with%20companies%20in%20its%20network%2C%20many%20of%20which%20offer%20tuition%20reimbursement.%20Over%20four%20years%2C%20students%20earn%20a%20wage%20and%20log%20the%20thousands%20of%20work%20hours%20required%20to%20become%20a%20licensed%20electrician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELabor%20unions%20like%20the%20International%20Brotherhood%20of%20Electrical%20Workers%20offer%20similar%20apprenticeship%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShmelzer%20said%20there%20are%20many%20%26quot%3Bcareer%20circuits%26quot%3B%20for%20electricians%2C%20including%20indoor%20construction%20and%20utility%20work%20as%20well%20as%20project%20management%20and%20design.%20In%20Virginia%2C%20at%20least%20500%20electricians%20are%20needed%20right%20now%20because%20commercial%20buildings%20are%20being%20renovated%20into%20apartments%20as%20more%20people%20work%20from%20home%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-centers-energy-grid-electricity-virginia-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20data%20centers%20are%20popping%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shmelzer%20said.%20Electricians%20are%20essential%20to%20all%20this%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20apprenticeship%20programs%20allow%20people%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families%20with%20great%20wages%2C%20little%20to%20no%20debt%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20career%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Shmelzer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-become-electrician-apprenticeship-job-growth-career-trend-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700328302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65551c034ca513d8242a181a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-become-electrician-apprenticeship-job-growth-career-trend-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20US%20races%20to%20meet%20green%20energy%20targets%2C%20it%20needs%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20electricians%20that%20will%20unlock%20the%20biggest%20economic%20transformation%20in%20a%20century.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-become-electrician-apprenticeship-job-growth-career-trend-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T-Mobile%20faces%20a%20lawsuit%20after%20an%20employee%20sent%20himself%20nude%20photos%20he%20found%20on%20a%20customer's%20phone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20T-Mobile%20store%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6558c5bb9c7d23cb3b9d109c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224243%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20T-Mobile%20store%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kappeler%2C%20Picture%20Alliance%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ET-Mobile%20is%20facing%20anot