lace%20that%20day%20and%20would%20need%20to%20pay%20to%20get%20the%20old%20device%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20pled%20guilty%20last%20month%20to%20charges%20of%20first-degree%20computer%20trespass%20and%20disclosing%20intimate%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20T-Mobile%20is%20also%20being%20sued%20by%20the%20victim%20for%20%26quot%3Bturning%20a%20blind%20eye%26quot%3B%20to%20employees%20that%20exploit%20their%20access%20to%20customer's%20sensitive%20data%20and%20failing%20to%20train%20them%20adequately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BT-Mobile%20has%20failed%20to%20implement%20any%20common-sense%20security%20hardware%20or%20software%20to%20protect%20consumers%20from%20their%20data%20and%20privacy%20being%20exploited%20during%20ordinary%20transactions%20at%20the%20T-Mobile%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20per%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20echoes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2022%2F05%2F19%2Fthe-modern-day-peeping-tom-how-creeps-steal-nudes-off-phones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20against%20T-Mobile%2C%20in%20which%20employees%20have%20downloaded%20intimate%20content%20from%20customers%20who%20had%20brought%20in%20old%20phones%20in%20for%20an%20upgrade%2C%20as%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20sued%20T-Mobile%20for%20its%20pattern%20and%20practice%20of%20incentivizing%20trade-ins%20knowing%20some%20of%20their%20pervs%20will%20steal%20customers'%20nudes%20and%20sex%20vids.%20The%20jig%20is%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcagoldberglaw%2Fstatus%2F1725632686482444547%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Carrie%20Goldberg%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20who%20filed%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type