%20and%20the%20booster%20on%20Starship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb1b23a39a1b00190b9e9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20vent%20and%20heat%20shields%20were%20added%20between%20the%20spaceship%20and%20the%20booster.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20hot-staging%2C%20we%20throttle%20down%20and%20shut%20down%20most%20of%20the%20booster%20engines.%20Then%20we%20light%20the%20Starship%20engines.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20efficient%20ways%20to%20do%20stage%20separation%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20a%20program%20update%20in%20October%2C%20per%20Aviation%20Week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20that's%20the%20riskiest%20part%20of%20the%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22blurry%20distant%20rocket%20firing%20engines%20bright%20with%20a%20blue%20purple%20trail%20in%20a%20dark%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6558edc322cf74a57399d4f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarship-Super%20Heavy%20just%20moments%20before%20separation%2C%20in%20a%20screengrab%20from%20SpaceX's%20livestream%20of%20the%20launch%20on%20X.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESuccessful%20hot%20staging%20and%20separation%20was%20the%20main%20goal%20for%20Saturday's%20launch%2C%20and%20Starship%20succeeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20crucial%20moment%2C%20the%20stages%20separately%20beautifully%2C%20with%20Super%20Heavy%20tumbling%20downward%20and%20Starship%20climbing%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20the%20booster%20exploded.%20That%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20surprise%20for%20this%20flight%2C%20but%20it's%20another%20wrinkle%20SpaceX%20will%20have%20to%20iron%20out%20since%20it%20wants%20to%20land%20its%20Super%20Heavy%20boosters%20in%2