%20military%20presence%20from%20the%20country.%20Sources%20in%20the%20ministry%20of%20external%20affairs%20said%20%26quot%3Bworkable%20solutions%26quot%3B%20are%20being%20discussed%20between%20the%20two%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20said%20Mr%20Muizzu%20formally%20made%20the%20request%20when%20he%20met%20Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20at%20the%20President's%20office%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%20Mr%20Rijiju%2C%20who%20is%20the%20minister%20of%20earth%20sciences%2C%20was%20in%20the%20country%20to%20attend%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20around%2070%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Maldives%2C%20manning%20radars%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft.%C2%A0Indian%20warships%20also%20help%20patrol%20the%20country's%20exclusive%20economic%20zone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20government%20sources%20said%20when%20Mr%20Rijiju%20called%20on%20Mr%20Muizzu%2C%20the%20president%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20present%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20aircraft%20for%20medical%20evacuation%20and%20anti-drug%20trafficking%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20President%20Muizzu%20acknowledged%20the%20contribution%20of%20these%20Indian%20helicopters%20and%20planes%20towards%20the%20medical%20evacuation%20of%20Maldivian%20citizens.%20They%20are%20also%20central%20to%20the%20confidence%20that%20international%20tourists%20have%20while%20staying%20on%20remote%20islands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20agreed%20that%20the%20two%20Governments%20would%20discuss%20workable%20solutions%20for%20continued%20cooperation%20through%20the%20use%20of%20these%20platforms%20as%20this%20serves%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20Promise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20of%20foreign%20troops%20from%20the%20archipelago%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20promises%20of%20the%20new%20president%20and%20he%20h