20rules%20and%20also%20laundering%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20news%20reports%20have%20underlined%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20had%20been%20eyeing%20the%20Krishnapatnam%20Port%20Company%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-inside-the-companys-growth-machine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20several%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20company%20of%20the%20Navayuga%20group%20during%20the%20TDP%20era.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Jagan%20Reddy%20then%20taking%20on%20the%20firm%2C%20Adani%20tried%20its%20luck%20once%20more%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esuccessfully%20acquired%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202020%2C%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20gave%20its%20consent%20to%20the%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zones%20to%20buy%20out%20a%2075%25%20stake%20in%20that%20port%20from%20Navayuga.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fadani-ports-takes-full-control-of-krishnapatnam-port%2Farticle34241716.ece%5C%22%3EThe%20remaining%2025%25%20was%20taken%20over%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPlum%20projects%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tunnel%20is%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20route%2C%20a%20pet%20project%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20completed%2C%20it%20would%20not%20only%20shorten%20the%20pilgrimage%20route%20to%20Yamunotri%20by%2020%20kms%2C%20but%20also%20enable%20all-weather%20connectivity%20to%20the%20major%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20site.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%2C%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%20committee%20on%20economic%20affairs%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%202018%2C%20was%20to%20be%20completed%20in%202022%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20currently%20on%20an%20extension.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20mid-2020%2C%20Navayuga%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbmcw.com%2Fnews%2Fnavayuga-group-bags-1-887-cr-rail-line-project.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20been%20granted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20Rishikesh-Karnaprayag%20rail%20link%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20project.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700325616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20details%20on%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company%20Limited%2C%20from%20which%2041%20workers%20remain%20trapped%20in%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20government's%20high-profile%20yet%20controversial%20Char%20Dham%20project%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%20are%20worth%20noting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hungary%20needs%20to%20change%20the%20EU%2C%20not%20leave%20it%3A%20PM%20Viktor%20Orban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700325536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105318743%2Cimgsize-609184.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungary-needs-to-change-the-eu-not-leave-it-pm-viktor-orban%2Farticleshow%2F105318716.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20borde