olitically%20vocal%20and%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20in%20its%20latest%20edition%20for%20attempting%20to%20tread%20carefully%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20faced%20criticism%20first%20from%20some%20Israeli%20and%20American%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20then%20from%20Palestinian%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EDeadline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20opening%20night%20ceremony%20of%20the%20festival%20last%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F11%2Finternational-documentary-festival-amsterdam-israel-gaza-controversy-1235612497%2F%5C%22%3Esaw%20three%20pro-Palestinian%20demonstrators%20interrupting%3C%2Fa%3E%20IDFA%20artistic%20director%20Orwa%20Nyrabia%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20carrying%20a%20banner%20bearing%20the%20controversial%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20River%20to%20the%20Sea%2C%20Palestine%20Will%20Be%20Free%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20viewed%20by%20many%20Jews%20as%20anti-Semitic%20and%20calling%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Nyrabia%20applauded%20the%20protesters%20on%20stage%2C%20he%20later%20issued%20a%20joint%20apology%20after%20facing%20criticism%20from%20members%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20film%20community%20as%20well%20as%20some%20documentary%20filmmakers%20in%20the%20US.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20apology%20then%20drew%20criticism%20from%20many%20Palestinian%20filmmakers%20including%20Basma%20al-Sharif%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20director%20and%20artist%20who%20withdrew%20a%20film%20at%20the%20festival.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinian%20filmmaker%20Jumana%20Manna%20also%20took%20to%20Instagram%20to%20announce%20the%20cancellation%20of%20her%20film%20at%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20acceptance%20speech%2C%20Patwardhan%20said%20that%20he%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%E2%80%9Camplify%20all%20international%20voices%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20ongoing%20war%20zones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisunderstood%20slogan%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20real%20meaning%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20call%20for%20a%20land%20where%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20Christians%20and%20all%20others%20can%20live%20together%20in%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20should%20be%20emphasised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatwardhan%20also%20lauded%20those%20who%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20those%20who%20stayed%20back%20to%20continue%20to%20debate%20and%20those%20who%20%E2%80%9Callowed%20the%20space%E2%80%9D%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20protests%20have%20been%20non-violent.%20Non-violence%20can%20build%20a%20global%20community.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20Palestinians%20and%20Jews%20are%20marching%20together%20with%20others%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20just%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20acceptance%20speech%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2FThe%20World%20is%20Family%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcceptance%20speech%20for%20Best%20Editing%20Award%20at%20IDFA%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20amplify%20all%20international%20voices%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20ongoing%20war%20zones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20misunderstood%20slogan.%20Some%20interpret%20it%20as%20a%20slogan%20calling%20for%20a%20One%20State%20solution%20and%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Jews.%20This%20misunderstanding%20is%20why%20the%20real%20meaning%20of%20the%20slogan%20should%20be%20explained%20and%20emphasized%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20a%20call%20for%20a%20land%20where%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20Christians%20and%20all%20others%20can%20live%20together%20in%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20applaud%20those%20who%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20festival%20and%20sparked%20an%20international%20debate.%20I%20applaud%20those%20who%20stayed%20back%20to%20continue%20the%20debate%20from%20within.%20And%20I%20applaud%20those%20who%20allowed%20us%20the%20space%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20protests%20have%20been%20non-violent.%20Non-violence%20can%20build%20a%20global%20community.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20Palestinians%20and%20Jews%20are%20marching%20together%20with%20others%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20just%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20world%20is%20enslaved%20by%20a%20global%20arms%20industry%20that%20profits%20from%20every%20war%20and%20from%20every%20death.%20It%20is%20from%20this%20slavery%20that%20our%20world%20must%20be%20set%20free.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20world%20is%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnand%20Patwardhan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E16%20November%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700325237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F25093726%2Fanand-patwardhan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fanand-patwardhan-idfa-immediate-ceasefire%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Filmm