%20banned%20products%20with%20a%20halal%20tag.%20Production%2C%20storage%2C%20distribution%2C%20and%20sale%20of%20food%20products%20with%20the%20Halal%20certification%20has%20been%20forbidden%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20said%20the%20state%20government.%20Products%20manufactured%20for%20export%2C%20however%2C%20will%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20legal%20measures%20will%20be%20implemented%20against%20any%20individual%20or%20firm%20engaged%20in%20the%20production%2C%20storage%2C%20distribution%2C%20buying%2C%20and%20selling%20of%20Halal-certified%20medicines%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20cosmetics%20within%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalal%20certification%20of%20food%20products%20is%20a%20parallel%20system%20which%20creates%20confusion%20regarding%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20items%20and%20is%20not%20tenable%20under%20Section%2089%20of%20the%20Food%20Law%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%2C%20the%20order%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20decide%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20items%20lies%20only%20with%20the%20authorities%20and%20institutions%20given%20in%20Section%2029%20of%20the%20said%20Act%2C%20who%20check%20the%20relevant%20standards%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20certain%20medicines%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20cosmetic%20products%20are%20reported%20to%20feature%20the%20Halal%20certificate%20on%20their%20packaging%20or%20labelling%20when%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bno%20provisions%20for%20marking%20Halal%20certification%20on%20labels%20in%20the%20government%20rules%20related%20to%20drugs%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20cosmetics%26quot%3B%2C%20nor%20is%20there%20any%20mention%20of%20Halal%20certification%20in%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Cosmetics%20Act%2C%201940%2C%20and%20its%20related%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20a%20police%20case%20was%20filed%C2%A0against%20a%20company%20and%20a%20few%20other%20organisations%20for%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bexploiting%20people's%20religious%20sentiments%26quot%3B%20to%20boost%20sales%20by%20providing%20%26quot%3Bforged%26quot%3B%20halal%20certificates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20entities%20such%20as%20the%20Halal%20India%20Private%20Limited%20Chennai%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%20Delhi%2C%20Halal%20Council%20of%20India%20Mumbai%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama%20Maharashtra%20and%20others%20for%20allegedly%20exploiting%20religious%20sentiments%20to%20boost%20sales%20by%20providing%20halal%20certificates%20to%20customers%20of%20a%20specific%20religion%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20raised%20concerns%20over%20a%20large-scale%20conspiracy%2C%20indicating%20attempts%20to%20allegedly%20decrease%20the%20sale%20of%20products%20from%20companies%20lacking%20the%20halal%20certificate%2C%20which%20is%20illegal%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20that%20these%20companies%20allegedly%20issued%20forged%20halal%20certificates%20to%20various%20companies%20for%20financial%20gains%2C%20fostering%20not%20only%20social%20animosity%20but%20also%20violating%20public%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20termed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20legal%20measures%20to%20counter%20such%20misinformation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalal%20certification%20is%20mentioned%20on%20the%20labels%20of%20certain%20food%20products%20like%20dairy%20products%2C%20sugar%20bakery%20products%2C%20peppermint%20oil%2C%20salty%20ready-to-eat%20savouries%20and%20edible%20oils%20etc%2C%20the%20food%20commissioner's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalal%20certification%20is%20a%20guarantee%20that%20the%20food%20is%20prepared%20in%20accordance%20with%20Islamic%20law%20and%20is%20unadulterated.%20If%20a%20product%20contains%20animals%20or%20animal%20byproducts%20that%20are%20considered%20prohibited%20under%20the%20law%2C%20then%20it%20cannot%20receive%20a%20halal%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20halal%20foods%20are%20those%20that%20are%20made%2C%20produced%2C%20manufactured%2C%20processed%2C%20and%20stored%20using%20machinery%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%2For%20utensils%20that%20have%20been%20cleaned%20according%20to%20Islamic%20law%20and%20are%20free%20from%20any%20component%20that%20Muslims%20are%20prohibited%20from%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700325060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8t2uficc_grocery-store_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bans-sale-of-halal-certified-products-with-immediate-effect-4585665%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20today%20banned%20products%20with%20halal%20tag.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bans-sale-of-halal-certified-products-with-immediate-effect-4585665%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bans-sale-of-halal-certified-products-with-immediate-effect-4585665%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bans-sale-of-halal-certified-products-with-immediate-effect-4585665%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mike%20Johnson%20warned%20the%20US%20was%20going%20down%20a%20'dark%20and%20depraved'%20path%20before%20he%20was%20named%20speaker%20and%20said%20the%20country%20'almost%20seems%20irredeemable'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Johnson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6