e%20the%20future%20of%20Telangana%20and%20India.%20Telangana%20was%20a%20surplus%20state%20when%20it%20was%20formed%2C%20but%20today%20KCR%20has%20put%20the%20state%20in%20a%20debt%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%203%20lakh%20crore.%20KCR%20has%20made%20Telangana%20a%20hub%20of%20corruption.%20BRS%20means%20-%20Bhrashtachar%20Rishwatkhori%20Samithi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Warangal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20in%20its%20Telangana%20manifesto%20said%20it%20will%20form%20a%20committee%20to%20draft%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20to%20consolidate%20and%20harmonise%20personal%20laws.%20It%20promised%20unconstitutional%20religion-based%20reservations%20will%20be%20scrapped%20and%20reservations%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20would%20be%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20Telangana%2C%20it%20will%20appoint%20a%20commission%20of%20enquiry%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20to%20look%20into%20all%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20including%20the%20Kaleswaram%20and%20Dharani%20scams%2C%20and%20other%20financial%20irregularities%20that%20allegedly%20happened%20under%20the%20BRS%20government%2C%20the%20manifesto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20promised%20four%20free%20cooking%20gas%20(LPG)%20cylinders%20every%20year%20to%20Ujwala%20scheme%20beneficiaries%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20party%2C%20if%20it%20wins%20in%20Telangana%2C%20will%20organise%20darshan%20trips%20to%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ayodhya%20for%20free.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20alleged%20the%20BRS%20government%20gave%20religion-based%20reservation%20to%20Muslims%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BReservation%20was%20given%20to%20Muslims%20by%20snatching%20it%20away%20from%20OBCs%20and%20STs%20under%20pressure%20from%20Owaisi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20AIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%202018%2C%20the%20ruling%20BRS%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(TRS)%2C%20won%2088%20of%20the%20119%20seats%2C%20grabbing%2047.4%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20vote%20share.%20The%20Congress%20came%20a%20distant%20second%20with%20just%2019%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20will%20vote%20on%20November%2030%3B%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700323440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fggaslthg_amit-shah_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-manifesto-bjp-promises-to-form-panel-to-probe-kcr-government-4585715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20in%20its%20manifesto%20for%20Telangana%20has%20promised%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20to%20go%20into%20alleged%20corruption%20by%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20KC%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-manifesto-bjp-promises-to-form-panel-to-probe-kcr-government-4585715%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-manifesto-bjp-promises-to-form-panel-to-probe-kcr-government-4585715%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-manifesto-bjp-promises-to-form-panel-to-probe-kcr-government-4585715%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAustralia%20Know%20How%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Yuvraj%20Singh's%20Warning%20To%20India%20Ahead%20Of%20Final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20all-rounder%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20feels%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20will%20only%20los