B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20captain%20Rohit%20also%20praised%20Australia%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20final%2C%20labelling%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20side%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20a%20very%20complete%20side.%20We%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20form%20they%20are%20in%20rather%20focus%20on%20our%20cricket%20and%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20at%20the%20pre-match%20presser.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700323260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F36n9olpo_team-india-afp_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-know-how-to-yuvraj-singhs-warning-to-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-final-4585319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unbeaten%20India%20square%20off%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20final%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-know-how-to-yuvraj-singhs-warning-to-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-final-4585319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-know-how-to-yuvraj-singhs-warning-to-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-final-4585319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Faustralia-know-how-to-yuvraj-singhs-warning-to-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-final-4585319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Schools%20To%20Reopen%20Monday%20As%20Pollution%20Levels%20Decline%3A%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20all%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20reopen%20from%20Monday%20following%20a%20decline%20in%20pollution%20levels.%20The%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SAFAR%20(System%20of%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Weather%20Forecasting%20And%20Research)%2C%20the%20average%20air%20quality%20index%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%20was%20317%2C%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20schools%20will%20reopen%2C%20the%20government%20said%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20ban%20on%20outdoor%20sports%20activities%20and%20morning%20assemblies%20for%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%208%2C%20after%20a%20dip%20in%20air%20quality%20and%20the%20enforcement%20of%20Stage%20IV%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%2C%20the%20education%20department%20had%20declared%20an%20early%20winter%20break%20from%20November%209-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20on%20reopening%20schools%20came%20hours%20after%20the%20improvement%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20from%20'severe'%20to%20'very%20poor'%20prompted%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20a%20statutory%20body%20responsible%20for%20formulating%20strategies%20to%20combat%20pollution%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20and%20adjoining%20areas%2C%20to%20order%20the%20removal%20of%20GRAP-IV%20curbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStage%20IV%20restrictions%2C%20which%20had%20been%20imposed%20on%20November%205%2C%20include%20a%20ban%20on%20all%20diesel%20four-wheelers%20except%20those%20vehicles%20that%20comply%20with%20BS-VI%20emission%20norms.%20All%20diesel-powered%20medium%20and%20heavy%20goods%20vehicles%2C%20except%20those%20used%20for%20essential%20or%20emergency%20services%2C%20had%20been%20banned%20from%20entering%20the%20national%20capital.%20These%20restrictions%20have%20now%20been%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFindings%20from%20a%20joint%20project%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20revealed%20that%20vehicular%20emissions%20accounted%20for%20about%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20national%20capital's%20air%20pollution%20on%20Friday.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20reduce%20to%2038%20per%20cent%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700323080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F44eh4798_delhi-pollution_625x300_04_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-from-monday-as-pollution-levels-decline-says-government-4585693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20all%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20reopen%20from%20Monday%20following%20a%20decline%20in%20pollution%20levels.%20The%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-from-monday-as-pollution-levels-decline-says-government-4585693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-from-monday-as-pollution-levels-decline-says-government-4585693%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-from-monday-as-pollution-levels-decline-says-government-4585693%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haley%20and%20Ramaswamy%20react%20differently%20to%20Trump's%20'vermin'%20remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700322548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105318356%2Cimgsize-950367.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-and-vivek-ramaswamy-react-differently-to-trumps-vermin-remark%2Farticleshow%2F105318318.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C