%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%20Johnson%20posted%20a%20photo%20of%20himself%2C%20his%20two%20daughters%20and%20Santorum%20posing%20with%20Duggar%2C%20calling%20the%20event%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20photo%2C%20from%20Johnson's%20campaign%20candidate%20account%2C%20featured%20a%20grinning%20Duggar%20on%20one%20side%2C%20with%20Johnson%20on%20the%20other%2C%20and%20Santorum%20in%20the%20center%2C%20flanked%20by%20children%20wearing%20Johnson's%20campaign%20T-shirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20great%20group%20of%20Godly%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20commented.%20%26quot%3BCharacter%20does%20count%2C%20and%20I%20thank%20each%20of%20you%20for%20being%20a%20living%20example%20to%20us%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuggar%20resigned%20in%20May%202015%2C%20after%20InTouch%20Magazine%20published%20accounts%20from%20police%20records%20in%202006%20accusing%20Duggar%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Johnson's%20spokesperson%20Raj%20Shah%20sought%20to%20put%20distance%20between%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Duggar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJosh%20Duggar%20is%20a%20criminal%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said%20in%20the%20emailed%20statement.%20%26quot%3BBusiness%20Insider's%20attempt%20to%20link%20Johnson%20to%20his%20misconduct%20based%20on%20a%20decade-old%20Facebook%20post%20about%20his%20attendance%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20prior%20to%20Duggar's%20conduct%20being%20exposed%20is%20quite%20ridiculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins%20issued%20a%20statement%20immediately%20following%20the%20revelations%20in%202015.%20%26quot%3BJosh%20believes%20that%20the%20situation%20will%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20be%20effective%20in%20his%20current%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20called%20the%20accusations%20%26quot%3Bpreviously%20unknown%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Washington%20Post%2C%20Perkins%20was%20close%20to%20Duggar's%20father%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjill-duggar-family-relationship-father-jim-bob-duggar-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJim%20Bob%20Duggar%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Arkansas%20House%20of%20Representatives%20from%201999%20to%202003.%20InTouch%20reported%20in%202015%2C%20citing%20police%20reports%2C%20that%20Jim%20Bob%20met%20with%20elders%20at%20his%20Arkansas%20church%20in%202003%20after%20learning%20about%20multiple%20sexual%20abuse%20claims%20involving%20Josh.%20But%20neither%20the%20senior%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FzqPMi%2314%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDuggar%20nor%20the%20church%20elders%20reported%20anything%20to%20the%20police%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuggar%20was%20never%20charged%20over%20the%20abuse%20alleged%20in%20the%20police%20reports%2C%20which%20fell%20outside%20of%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations.%20He%20is%20now%20serving%2012%20and%20half%20years%20in%20prison%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20possessing%20child%20pornography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuggar%20isn't%20the%20only%20figure%20associated%20with%20Perkins%20and%20the%20FRC%20that%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20minors.%20In%202010%2C%20Johnson%20was%20tapped%20to%20be%20the%20inaugural%20dean%20of%20the%20new%20Christian-oriented%20Paul%20Pressler%20School%20of%20Law%20at%20Louisiana%20College.%20Pressler%2C%20a%20retired%20judge%20and%20leader%20in%20the%20Southern%20Baptist%20Convention%2C%20was%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20shifting%20the%20Baptist%20church%20rightward%20in%20the%201980s.%20Perkins%20sat%20on%20the%20school's%20board%20of%20trustees%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-johnson-louisiana-college-law-school-resignation-fallout-internal-memo-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elaw%20school%20never%20opened%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Johnson%20resigned%20in%202012.%20Five%20years%20later%2C%20in%202017%2C%20a%20former%20Bible%20study%20student%20of%20Pressler's%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20alleging%20that%20the%20church%20leader%20began%20sexually%20abusing%20him%20when%20he%20was%2014%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20sworn%20testimony%20and%20emails%20unearthed%20in%20lawsuits%20have%20indicated%20that%20church%20leaders%20and%20local%20GOP%20politicians%20were%20aware%20of%20allegations%20that%20Pressler%20had%20abused%20minors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baptiststandard.com%2Fnews%2Ftexas%2Fcourt-documents-shed-light-on-allegations-against-pressler%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20far%20back%20as%202004%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Perkins%20himself%20knew%20about%20the%20allegations%20against%20Pressler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20evidence%20that%20Perkins%20knew%20of%20another%20case%20of%20an%20associate%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20sexual%20impropriety%20involving%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20keep%20it%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20according%20to%20emails%20obtained%20by%20the%20Washington%20Post%2C%20the%20father%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20college%20student%20attending%20a%20meeting%20for%20the%20Council%20for%20National%20Policy%20told%20Perkins%20that%20Wesley%20Goodman%2C%20a%20young%20Ohio%20conservative%20politician%20and%20Perkins%20acolyte%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-a-conservative-group-dealt-with-a-fondling-charge-against-a-rising-gop-star%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2Fb3b4b8da-c956-11e7-b0cf-7689a9f2d84e_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egroped%20the%20young%20man%20in%20his%20sleep%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins%20urged%20Goodman%20not%20to%20run%20for%20office%20but%20never%20made%20the%20incident%20public%2C%20even%20after%20Goodman%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Ohio%20state%20legislature%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%20Goodman%20later%20resigned%20after%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fwes-goodman-ohio-republican.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eunrelated%20incident%20of%20%26quot%3Binappropriate%26quot%3B%20sexual%20behavior%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20his%20office%2C%20according%20to%20statements%20from%20the%20Ohio%20state%20speaker%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins%20was%20president%20of%20the%20CNP%2C%20a%20secretive%20group%20of%20far-right%20conservatives%20that%20participated%20in%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20Perkins%20has%20been%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwashingtonspectator.org%2Fhow-christian-nationalists-big-oil-and-the-big-lie-seized-the-speakers-gavel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20%26quot%3Binstrumental%26quot%3B%20in%20shaping%20the%20CNP'%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Es%20recent%20agenda%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CNP's%20own%20internal%20newsletter%20first%20as%20reported%20by%20The%20Washington%20Spectator%2C%20including%20pushing%20for%20anti-LGBTQ%20and%20anti-abortion%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20Johnson's%20spokesman%2C%20said%20Johnson%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20claims%20regarding%20Pressler%20or%20Goodman.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Speaker%20had%20no%20knowledge%20of%20accusations%20against%20Paul%20Pressler%20and%20has%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20Wesley%20Goodman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20pathetic%20attempt%20at%20a%20hit%20job%20takes%20guilt%20by%20association%20to%20a%20new%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalls%20and%20emails%20to%20Perkins%20and%20Duggar%20family%20lawyers%20were%20not%20immediately%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPressler%20and%20Goodman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-speaker-mike