%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20a%20map%20has%20emerged%20that%20points%20to%20an%20alleged%20serious%20lapse%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20company%20involved%20in%20its%20construction.%20According%20to%20the%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%2C%20all%20tunnels%20over%203%20km%20long%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20an%20escape%20route%20to%20rescue%20people%20in%20case%20there%20is%20a%20calamity.%20The%20map%20proves%20that%20such%20an%20escape%20route%20was%20also%20planned%20for%20the%204.5%20km%20Silkyara%20tunnel%2C%20but%20never%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%20are%20now%20also%20coming%20up%20with%20alternative%20plans%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%2C%20who%20have%20been%20stranded%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20since%20Sunday%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20of%20the%2041%20construction%20workers%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20migrants%2C%20are%20now%20beginning%20to%20worry%20after%20the%20American%20auger%2C%20or%20drill%20machine%2C%20also%20stopped%20working%20on%20Friday%20evening%20after%20a%20loud%20%26quot%3Bcracking%20sound%26quot%3B%20was%20heard%20in%20the%20tunnel.%20Some%20of%20the%20family%20members%20and%20other%20workers%20involved%20in%20the%20construction%20said%20the%20labourers%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20by%20now%20if%20the%20escape%20route%20had%20been%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20escape%20routes%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20even%20after%20tunnels%20are%20built%20to%20rescue%20people%20passing%20through%20them%20in%20vehicles%20if%20there%20is%20a%20collapse%2C%20landslide%20or%20any%20other%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20was%20displayed%20when%20Union%20Minister%20VK%20Singh%20had%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20tunnel%20collapse%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20workers%20would%20be%20rescued%20in%20two-three%20days.%20The%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20road%20transport%20and%20highways%20had%20said%20the%20rescue%20could%20be%20finished%