n%20is%20exploring%20whether%20a%20hole%20can%20be%20drilled%20vertically%2C%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20rock%20that%20the%20tunnel%20is%20passing%20through%2C%20and%20get%20the%20workers%20out%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20plan%2C%20suggested%20by%20the%20railways%2C%20is%20digging%20a%20parallel%20tunnel%20horizontally%2C%20but%20from%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20rock.%20This%20tunnel%20would%20intersect%20with%20the%20main%20tunnel%20at%20the%20point%20where%20the%20workers%20are%20trapped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamilies%20Anxious%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Some%20family%20members%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20said%20they%20are%20losing%20hope.%20The%20brother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20workers%20said%20they%20need%20to%20be%20rescued%20quickly%20before%20their%20health%20deteriorates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20prolonged%20confinement%20may%20affect%20their%20physical%20and%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700316180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F63m0786g_uttarakhand-tunnel-escape-route_625x300_18_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-lapse-escape-route-was-planned-for-uttarakhand-tunnel-but-not-built-4585299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20160%20hours%20since%2041%20workers%20got%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20a%20map%20has%20emerged%20that%20points%20to%20an%20alleged%20serious%20lapse%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20company%20involved%20in%20its%20construction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-lapse-escape-route-was-planned-for-uttarakhand-tunnel-but-not-built-4585299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2