ing%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20the%20AI%20boom%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20change%20a%20core%20tenet%20of%20investing%20for%20the%20basic%2C%20moderate-risk%20investor%3A%20the%2060%2F40%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20allocate%2060%25%20of%20your%20portfolio%20in%20stocks%2C%2040%25%20in%20bonds%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20touted%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20investing%20since%20the%201950s%2C%20but%20it's%20come%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fblackrock-vanguard-60-40-portfolio-stocks-bonds-funds-investing-analysis-2023-4%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20doubt%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20now%2C%20another%20wrinkle%20in%20the%20debate%20is%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20technology%20could%20to%20boost%20productivity%20so%20much%20that%20the%20correlations%20between%20growth%20and%20inflation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20one%20between%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20might%20flip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20diffusion%20acts%20like%20a%20supply%20shock%2C%20boosting%20growth%20and%20often%20reducing%20inflation%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20wrote%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20prior%20assumptions%20about%20how%20to%20diversify%20risk%20may%20no%20longer%20apply%20as%20the%20AI%20boom%20will%20spell%20healthy%20returns%20on%20both%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20%E2%80%94%20breaking%20the%20negative%20correlation%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20undermines%20a%20key%20piece%20of%20the%2060%2F40%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20bonds%20%E2%80%94%20as%20was%20the%20case%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20good%20diversifier%20they%20have%20been%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%2Fbond%20correlations%20vs%20growth%2Finflation%2