ic%20meeting%20in%20Nagaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20when%20the%20time%20of%20elections%20has%20come%2C%20these%20people%20are%20reluctantly%20getting%20themselves%20photographed%20together...%20Big%20leaders%20from%20Delhi%20come%20here%20and%20make%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20another%20leader%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20shake%20hands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20century%20of%20handshakes%20in%20five%20years%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20reconciliation.%20These%20people%20are%20pretending%20to%20join%20hands%20but%20there%20is%20bitterness%20in%20their%20hearts%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20given%20nothing%20but%20betrayal%20to%20the%20people%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20side%20is%20the%20Congress%20with%20a%20licence%20to%20loot%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20side%20it's%20Modi's%20guarantee%20card.%20Whom%20do%20you%20trust%3F%20If%20the%20whole%20country%20trusts%20Modi's%20guarantee%20card%2C%20there%20are%20some%20solid%20reasons%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20devoting%20every%20moment%20of%20day%20and%20night%20to%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20you%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20attacking%20each%20other%20during%20the%20high-pitch%20campaign%20for%20the%20November%2025%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20had%20guaranteed%20that%20Article%20370%20would%20be%20removed%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Did%20Modi%20fulfil%20the%20guarantee%20or%20not%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20ban%20on%20triple%20talaq%20and%20the%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20alleged%2