cials%20and%20animal%20rights%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20lady%20Kim%20Keon%20Hee%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20dog%20meat%20consumption%20and%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%2C%20has%20adopted%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-dog%20meat%20bills%20have%20failed%20in%20the%20past%20because%20of%20protests%20by%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20worries%20about%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20farmers%20and%20restaurant%20owners.%20Eating%20dog%20meat%20has%20been%20an%20age-old%20practice%20on%20the%20Korean%20peninsula%20and%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20beat%20the%20summer%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20much%20less%20common%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20though%20it%20is%20still%20eaten%20by%20some%20older%20people%20and%20served%20in%20certain%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnimal%20rights%20groups%20welcomed%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20ban.%20%26quot%3BA%20dream%20come%20true%20for%20all%20of%20us%20who%20have%20campaigned%20so%20hard%20to%20end%20this%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20Humane%20Society%20International%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20about%20dog%201%2C150%20breeding%20farms%2C%2034%20slaughter%20houses%2C%20219%20distribution%20companies%2C%20and%20some%201%2C600%20restaurants%20serving%20dog%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gallup%20Korea%20poll%20last%20year%20showed%2064%25%20opposed%20to%20dog%20meat%20consumption.%20The%20survey%20found%20only%208%25%20of%20respondents%20had%20eaten%20dog%20within%20the%20past%20year%2C%20down%20from%2027%25%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Reuters)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700310060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fle5aqq88_dogs-pay-close-attention-to-indications-from-humans_625x300_18_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld