.08.52-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20politician%20gives%20up%20power%20willingly.%20But%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20gone%20further%20than%20any%20political%20leader%20India%20has%20known%20to%20prove%20the%20truth%20of%20this%20dictum.%20From%20his%20first%20year%20in%20office%2C%20he%20has%20targeted%20every%20political%20leader%2C%20every%20political%20party%2C%20and%20every%20institution%20that%20could%20become%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20ambition%2C%20which%20is%20clearly%20to%20stay%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20natural%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParadoxically%2C%20the%20party%20he%20seems%20to%20fear%20the%20most%20is%20the%20smallest%20among%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20major%20constituents%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20animosity%20towards%20it%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20it%20routed%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%202015%20Delhi%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20winning%2067%20out%20of%20the%2070%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20four%20years%2C%20Modi%20has%20stopped%20at%20nothing%20in%20his%20bid%20to%20discredit%20the%20Delhi%20state%20government%20and%20force%20it%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20When%20the%20Kejriwal%20government%20changed%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20licensing%20policy%20in%202021%2C%20he%20and%20his%20advisers%20thought%20they%20had%20found%20the%20Achilles%E2%80%99%20heel%20that%20they%20had%20been%20looking%20for.%20Liquor%20is%20not%20only%20the%20cash%20cow%20of%20all%20state%20governments%20in%20the%20country%2C%20contributing%20up%20to%2020%25%20of%20their%20annual%20revenues%2C%20but%20also%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20sources%20of%20kickbacks%20to%20state%20government%20lawmakers%20and%20administrators%20for%20favours%20granted%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Liquor%20Mafia%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20deputy%20chief%