decision%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20resignations%20of%20Hoskote%20and%20Ettinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dynamics%20of%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20with%20their%20unchallenged%20media%20and%20public%20discrediting%20of%20our%20colleague%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%2C%20which%20forced%20him%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20make%20us%20very%20doubtful%20if%20this%20prerequisite%20for%20any%20coming%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20is%20currently%20given%20in%20Germany.%20Art%20requires%20a%20critical%20and%20multi-perspective%20examination%20of%20its%20diverse%20forms%20and%20contents%20to%20be%20able%20to%20resonate%20and%20develop%20its%20transformative%20capacity.%20Categorical%2C%20one-sided%20reductions%20and%20over-simplifications%20of%20complex%20contexts%20threaten%20to%20nip%20any%20such%20examination%20in%20the%20bud%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoskote%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%5C%22%3Eresignation%3C%2Fa%3E%20followed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sueddeutsche.de%2Fkultur%2Franjit-hoskote-documenta-antisemitismus-bds-1.6301063%3Freduced%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20daily%20%3Cem%3ES%C3%BCddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20November%209%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20a%202019%20letter%20signed%20by%20Hoskote%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdocumenta-committee-resigns-in-wake-of-antisemitism-claims%2Fa-67406086%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclearly%20antisemitic%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20culture%20minister%20Claudia%20Roth%20threatened%20to%20withdraw%20public%20funding%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20letter%20was%20published%20as%20part%20of%20the%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3ESuddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20circulated%20by%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%2C%20and%20Sanctions%20(BDS)%20global%20movement%2C%20aimed%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%20and%20adhere%20to%20human%20rights%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEttinger%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%20was%20unrelated%20to%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Hoskote.%20%3Cem%3EARTnews%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20her%20decision%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times%E2%80%9D%20affecting%20her%20country%2C%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20they%20understand%20that%20in%20view%20of%20its%20past%2C%20Germany%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdistinct%20social%20and%20political%20responsibilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20great%20sensitivity%20towards%20all%20anti-Semitic%20tendencies%20bears%20eloquent%20witness%20to%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20nation%20has%20internalised%20this%20responsibility.%20The%20ongoing%20fulfilment%20of%20this%20very%20responsibility%20deserves%20the%20greatest%20appreciation%2C%20especially%20now%2C%20when%20alarming%20signs%20of%20deep-rooted%20anti-Semitism%20are%20once%20again%20making%20themselves%20felt%20around%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20however%2C%20this%20awareness%20of%20special%20responsibilities%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20misused%20for%20opinion%20politics%20in%20order%20to%20suppress%20undesirable%20approaches%20and%20their%20broad%20and%20open%20discussion%20right%20from%20the%20start.%20Instead%20of%20debate%20and%20discussion%2C%20over-simplification%20and%20prejudgments%20are%20thus%20all%20too%20easily%20substituted%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20edition%20as%20well%2C%20the%20exhibition%20was%20engulfed%20in%20a%20scandal%20around%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20to%20BDS%20and%20a%20dispute%20over%20anti-Semitic%20iconography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20members%20said%20in%20the%20letter%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20this%20emotional%20and%20intellectual%20climate%20of%20over-simplification%20of%20complex%20realities%20and%20its%20resulting%20restrictive%20limitations%2C%20which%20has%20been%20prevalent%20since%20documenta15%20and%20especially%20against%20the%20background%20of%20the%20current%20crises%20our%20world%20is%20facing%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20conceive%20of%20a%20strong%20and%20signal%20exhibition%20project%2C%20and%20consequently%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20responsible%20continuation%20of%20the%20selection%20process%20to%20determine%20a%20curatorial%20concept%20for%20documenta16.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organisers%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20the%20task%20of%20inviting%20pioneering%20figures%20in%20contemporary%20art%20to%20apply%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Artistic%20Direction%20of%20documenta%2016%2C%20and%20to%20select%20the%20most%20promising%20format%20from%20the%20concepts%20presented.%20Appointment%20of%20the%20Artistic%20Direction%20is%20targeted%20for%20late%202023%20%2F%20early%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20current%20developments%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20%E2%80%9Copen%20exchange%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20circumstances%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20space%20in%20Germany%20for%20an%20open%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20the%20development%20of%20complex%20and%20nuanced%20artistic%20approaches%20that%20documenta%20artists%20and%20curators%20deserve.%20We%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20acceptable%20conditions%20can%20be%20created%20in%20short%20term%20and%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20disrespectful%20of%20documenta%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20simply%20remain%20content%20with%20the%20current%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20four%20members%E2%80%99%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%2C%20Ettinger%20had%20also%20stepped%20down%C2%A0%20for%20reasons%20that%20she%20stated%20were%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20against%20Hoskote%20but%20because%20Israel%20was%20enduring%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700301880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18153253%2Fimage-1520.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20author%20and%20curator%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%20resigned%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%C2%A0for%20the%20upcoming%2016th%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20in%20Kassel%2C%20Germany%20last%20week%20amid%20accusations%20of%20'anti-Semitism'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Says%20He%E2%80%99s%20Suing%20Media%20Matters%20Over%20Reports%20That%20Found%20X%2FTwitter%20Ads%20Ran%20Next%20to%20Pro-Nazi%2C%20White-Pride%20Posts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700301625000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2FElon-Musk.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235798786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20spate%20of%20major%20advertisers%20said%20they