n%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17164343%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20sleuths%20of%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20suddenly%20descended%20on%20human%20rights%20defender%20and%20school%20teacher%20Abdul%20Wahid%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20house%20on%20October%2011%2C%20he%20knew%20exactly%20what%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20next.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20been%20monitoring%20the%20three%20CCTVs%20that%20are%20installed%20on%20the%20front%20and%20the%20rear%20of%20his%20house%20%E2%80%93%20a%20chawl%20in%20Vikhroli%2C%20a%20densely%20populated%20area%20in%20suburban%20Mumbai.%20The%20cameras%20told%20him%20that%20a%20group%20of%20men%20and%20women%20%E2%80%93%20some%20dressed%20in%20Mumbai%20police%E2%80%99s%20uniform%20and%20a%20few%20in%20civil%20clothes%20%E2%80%93%20had%20converged%20outside%20his%20house.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20armed%20and%20few%20others%20with%20batons%20were%20aggressively%20banging%20at%20the%20door%20asking%20him%20to%20immediately%20let%20them%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20police%20had%20landed%20at%20his%20place%20at%205%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20440px)%2085vw%2C%20440px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20832w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM-292x300.png%20292w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAbdul%20Wahid%20Shaikh%20at%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20policemen%20discovered%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20they%20began%20hitting%20it%20with%20their%20batons%2C%20destroying%20one%20of%20them%20mounted%20right%20over%20the%20door.%20This%20action%20was%20captured%20by%20the%20adjacent%20CCTV%20camera.%20Shaikh%2C%20holed%20up%20in%20his%20house%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%2C%20kept%20pleading%20with%20the%20police%20to%20stop%20destroying%20his%20property%20and%20simply%20show%20them%20an%20official%20notice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20the%2020%20other%20locations%20that%20the%20NIA%20team%20had%20reached%20the%20same%20day%2C%20to%20raid%20houses%20and%20also%20simultaneously%20arrest%20people%20in%20the%20ongoing%20probe%20against%20alleged%20Popular%20Front%20of%20India%20(PFI)%20members%2C%20and%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20and%20anti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20raid%20at%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20received%20maximum%20traction%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20One%20reason%20is%20that%20Shaikh%2C%20who%20has%20already%20endured%20nine%20long%20years%20of%20incarceration%20(only%20to%20be%20later%20acquitted%20by%20the%20trial%20court)%2C%20is%20a%20well%20known%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20reason%2C%20and%20more%20plausible%20in%20this%20case%2C%20is%20that%20Shaikh%20was%20able%20to%20immediately%20substantiate%20his%20fear%20and%20accusations%20of%20police%20excess%20with%20ample%20video%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECollection%20of%20evidence%2C%20and%20the%20need%20to%20satiate%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20requirement%20of%20%E2%80%9Cproving%20one%E2%80%99s%20innocence%E2%80%9D%20even%20when%20one%20is%20not%20implicated%20in%20any%20criminal%20case%2C%20however%2C%20has%20come%20at%20a%20huge%20cost%2C%20Shaikh%20says.%20The%20one%20that%20hurts%20him%20and%20his%20family%20the%20most%20is%20the%20absolute%20compromise%20of%20their%20personal%20space%20and%20privacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisits%20without%20reason%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%20court%20in%202015%20acquitted%20him%20of%20all%20charges%20in%20the%20July%2011%2C%202006%20serial%20train%20blast%20case.%20Although%20his%20defence%20team%20was%20able%20to%20prove%20his%20innocence%20in%20the%20court%2C%20the%20police%20visits%20without%20any%20particular%20reason%2C%20summons%20to%20nearby%20police%20stations%20have%20continued%20over%20years.%20Shaikh%20knew%20if%20he%20had%20to%20ensure%20he%20does%20not%20end%20up%20in%20jail%20again%2C%20he%20had%20to%20put%20himself%20under%20constant%20watch.%20And%20not%20just%20him%2C%20but%20also%20his%20wife%20Sajida%20Tabassum%20and%20two%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20the%20two%20cameras%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20he%20was%20also%20compelled%20to%20install%20a%20camera%20in%20the%20living%20room%20of%20his%20modest%20flat.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20camera%20was%20installed%20to%20ensure%20that%20police%20follow%20the%20due%20process%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20house%20and%20do%20not%20harass%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20wife%2C%20who%20practices%20purdah%2C%20was%20opposed%20to%20this%20initially.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20complained%20of%20not%20feeling%20at%20ease%20inside%20her%20own%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDisturbing%20it%20may%20be%2C%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20is%20still%20not%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20case.%20Many%20individuals%2C%20predictably%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20who%20have%20faced%20police%20atrocity%20and%20the%20brutalities%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20carceral%20system%2C%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20putting%20themselves%20under%20CCTV%20surveillance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState-imposed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20discourse%20around%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20in%20India%20is%20at%20a%20crucial%20point%2C%20here%20is%20a%20large%20community%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%20facing%20both%20police%20excesses%20and%20fake%20criminal%20charges%20%E2%80%93%20forced%20to%20forsake%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20privacy.%20While%20the%20state%20might%20not%20be%20explicitly%20seen%20indulging%20in%20surveillance%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20it%20still%20is%20a%20state-imposed%20surveillance%2C%20says%2039-year-old%20Mohammad%20Bilal%20Gulam%20Rasul%20Kagazi%20from%20Surat%20district%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKagazi%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20who%20focuses%20on%20cases%20of%20tribal%20rights%2C%20has%20long%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20police%20vendetta.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20his%20legal%20practice%2C%20Kagazi%20has%20been%20fighting%20cases%20for%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20of%20the%20region%2C%20raising%20issues%20of%20police%20atrocities%20and%20land%20encroachment%2C%20among%20others.%20And%20in%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20state%20began%20looking%20at%20him%20as%20an%20adverse%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Kagazi%20has%20had%20multiple%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%2C%20all%20directly%20relating%20to%20his%20lawyering%20and%20activism%20in%20the%20region.%20In%202019%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsurat-advocate-alleges-harassment-for-taking-up-cases-against-police-officials%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20published%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20Kagazi%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20police%20harassment%20he%20had%20been%20facing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKagazi%2C%20too%2C%20has%20had%20to%20install%20cameras%20all%20around%20his%20house.%20These%20cameras%2C%20he%20says%2C%20visibly%20infringe%20on%20his%20privacy.%20But%20they%20also%20help%20provide%20him%20with%20some%20sense%20of%20security.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20too%20are%20apprehensive%20of%20barging%20into%20my%20house%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Burden%20of%20innocence%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20unrest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20and%20two%20other%20imminent%20countrywide%20exercises%2C%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20grew%20in%202019%2C%20many%20Muslim%20families%20felt%20that%20they%20could%20no%20longer%20rely%20on%20the%20state%20for%20their%20security%20for%20it%20was%20the%20state%20machinery%20they%20feared%20the%20most.%20Incidents%20of%20houses%20being%20raided%20both%20by%20the%20police%20and%20local%20Hindu%20thugs%20were%20rampant%20during%20that%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Khalapar%2C%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20locality%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20almost%20every%20house%20decided%20to%20instal%20cameras%20in%20and%20around%20them.%20Khalapar%2C%20where%20relatively%20well%20off%20Muslim%20families%20reside%2C%20ended%20up%20spending%20on%20an%20average%20Rs%2030-40%2C000%20in%20getting%20the%20installations%20done.%20Today%2C%20activist%20Ravish%20Babu%20says%2C%20the%20entire%20region%20is%20under%20a%20%E2%80%9Cself-%20imposed%20surveillance%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBabu%20%E2%80%93%20a%20law%20student%20and%20a%20young%20activist%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20who%20organised%20many%20anti-CAA%20protests%20in%20the%20district%20%E2%80%93%20too%20had%20to%20get%20multiple%20cameras%20installed%20around%20his%20two-storey%20house%20after%20the%20local%20police%20frequently%20visited%20his%20house%20and%20allegedly%20harassed%20both%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members.%20Along%20with%20deterring%20the%20police%2C%20Babu%20says%2C%20he%20is%20also%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20physical%20movement%20if%20that%20was%20to%20ever%20be%20necessary.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20proving%20one%E2%80%99s%20innocence%20is%20no%20more%20on%20the%20state%20but%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20self%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202017%2C%20in%20a%20historical%20ruling%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20privacy%E2%80%99%20is%20protected%20as%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty%20under%20Article%2021%20and%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fundamental%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20surrender%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivacy%20is%20a%20constitutional%20core%20of%20human%20dignity.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20right%20to%20privacy%20should%20ensure%20preservation%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20personal%20space%2C%20along%20with%20the%20inviolability%20of%20marriage%2C%20procreation%2C%20the%20home%20and%20even%20sexual%20orientation.%20But%20by%20putting%20themselves%20under%20the%20constant%20watch%20of%20pervasive%20cameras%2C%20individuals%20are%20forced%20to%20surrender%20their%20privacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20fashionable%20about%20installing%20so%20many%20cameras%20in%20and%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20says%20a%20young%20lawyer%20from%20rural%20Maharashtra.%20A%20Muslim%20man%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20a%20decade%20ago%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20terror%20module%2C%20he%20studied%20law%20after%20his%20release.%20He%20too%20had%20had%20cameras%20installed%20everywhere%20around%20him.%20But%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20completed%20law%20and%20began%20practicing%20in%20a%20local%20court%2C%20he%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20cameras.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20can%20use%20my%20court%20appearance%20as%20evidence%20that%20I%20am%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20anti-national%20activities%2C%20that%20the%20police%20are%20ever%20willing%20to%20implicate%20me%20and%20many%20educated%20men%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685237%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZainab%20(centre%2C%20in%20yellow).%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20matter%20how%20%E2%80%9Ccreepy%E2%80%9D%20it%20may%20be%2C%20cameras%20have%20for%20long%20provided%20a%20sense%20of%20security%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20says%20Zainab%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20Lucknow-based%20activist.%20When%20her%20family%20was%20targeted%20in%202019%20for%20actively%20participating%20in%20the%20anti-CAA%20and%20anti-NRC%20protests%2C%20Zainab%20had%20filmed%20the%20police%20atrocity%20on%20her%20phone.%20Her%20father%20was%20arrested%20and%20her%20then%20minor%20brother%20was%20illegally%20detained%20by%20the%20police.%20Zainab%20had%20made%20the%20videos%20public%20soon%20after.%20They%20garnered%20hu