20common%20thread%20in%20the%20discussions%20at%20the%20second%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20referring%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20challenges%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20geopolitical%20crisis%20that%20have%20caused%20thousands%20of%20deaths%20over%20the%20last%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20(November%2017)%2C%20India%20held%20the%20second%20virtual%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit.%20The%20first%20summit%20was%20held%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20It%20was%20part%20of%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20positioning%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20developing%20world%20ahead%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20opening%20session%20for%20leaders%2C%20Modi%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20all%20seeing%20that%20new%20challenges%20are%20emerging%20from%20events%20in%20the%20West%20Asia%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20India%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccondemned%20the%20heinous%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Israel%20on%20October%207%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20leader%20then%20noted%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20also%20called%20for%20restraint%20as%20well%20as%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20deaths%20of%20civilians%20in%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20After%20talking%20to%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20we%20have%20also%20sent%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20speak%20with%20one%20voice%20for%20the%20greater%20global%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2012%2C000%20civilians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F10%2F28%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-invasion-under-way-as-gaza-cut-off-from-the-world%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gaza%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counter-strikes%2C%20following%20Hamas%20attack%20that%20left%20over%201%2C400%20Israelis%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20most%20of%20the%20global%20south%20had%20spoken%20rather%20unanimously%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20when%20it%20passed%20a%20resolution%20on%20October%2027%2C%20calling%20for%20humanitarian%20pauses%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20Among%20the%20global%20south%2C%20the%20only%20major%20outliers%20had%20been%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20who%20had%20abstained%2C%20while%20most%20of%20Asia%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20Latin%20Africa%20voted%20yes%20on%20the%20resolution%20tabled%20by%20Jordan%20and%20the%20Arab%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20told%20reporters%20that%20all%20the%20leaders%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20concern%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20leaders%20spoke%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20leaders%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20terrorism%2C%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20horror%20at%20the%20civilian%20casualties%20due%20to%20the%20conflict.%20These%20three%20were%20the%20threads%20that%20were%20sort%20of%20common%20to%20all%20the%20interventions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20late%20night%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%20also%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20discussion%20on%20the%20need%20to%20have%20access%20to%20sustainable%20credit%2C%20which%20did%20not%20add%20to%20the%20debt%20burden%20of%20most%20countries.%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20topic%20was%20an%20indictment%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20policy%2C%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20no%20names%20were%20taken%2C%20but%20that%20there%20was%20acknowledgement%20on%20what%20kind%20of%20funding%20was%20not%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20essentially%20spoke%20of%20the%20need%20that%20when%20they%20access%20this%20financing%20for%20their%20development%20projects%20for%20climate%20crisis%20or%20for%20energy%20transitions%2C%20it%20should%20be%20in%20a%20manner%20and%20of%20a%20kind%20that%20does%20not%20impose%20a%20debt%20burden%20on%20the%20structural%20parameters%20of%20the%20economy.%20It%20should%20be%20more%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20session%20for%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20there%20continued%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20resistance%20for%20a%20greater%20role%20for%20the%20global%20south%20in%20shaping%20solutions%20for%20the%20key%20issues%20of%20our%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20lesson%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20perils%20of%20dependence%20for%20basic%20necessities%20on%20far%20away%20geographies%20abilities%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20economic%20concentrations%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20not%20only%20democratise%20and%20diversify%20production%2C%20but%20build%20resilient%20and%20reliable%20supply%20chains%20and%20promote%20local%20solutions.%20Only%20then%20can%20the%20global%20south%20secure%20its%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700287920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18114014%2Fimage-1518.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-indias-summit-for-global-south-leaders-raise-strong-concern-over-ongoing-conflict-in-west-asia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20second%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20referred%20to%20'new%20challenges'%20from%20the%20geopolitical%20crisis%20that%20have%20caused%20thousands%20of%20deaths%20over%20the%20last%20one%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-indias-summit-for-glob