a.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclicked%20the%20picture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20visiting%20a%20tamarind%20grove%20at%20Nalluru%20along%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20his%20friends.%20We%20stopped%20by%20the%20Gopalaswamy%20Temple%20to%20admire%20the%20carvings%20of%20Lord%20Krishna.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20spotted%20the%20spider%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20first%20thought%20was%2C%20how%20well-positioned%20the%20arachnid%20was.%20It%20almost%20seemed%20entranced%20by%20Lord%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20flute.%20Insects%2C%20particularly%20spiders%2C%20had%20always%20held%20a%20fancy%20for%20Vihaan%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20they%20spin%20webs%2C%20and%20hunt%20their%20prey%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20so%20cool%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20He%20recalls%20spending%20hours%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332890%2Findian-photographers-pictures-military-navy-wildlife-oceans-astronomy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapturing%20their%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20childhood%20summer%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20was%20only%20natural%20that%20the%20young%20boy%20sat%20down%2C%20and%20watched%20the%20spider%20weave%20a%20wheel-shaped%20web%2C%20entangling%20any%20prey%20that%20dared%20to%20come%20too%20close.%20And%20soon%20he%20got%20clicking.%20%E2%80%9CI%20must%20have%20clicked%20over%20200%20pictures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20among%20them%20was%20the%20winning%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%